  "path": "atlas/triggers/aws-eventbridge",
  "product": "atlas",
  "title": "Send Trigger Events to AWS EventBridge",
  "description": "MongoDB offers an AWS Eventbridge\npartner event source that lets you send Atlas Trigger events to an event bus\ninstead of calling an Atlas Function. You can configure any Trigger type to\nsend events to EventBridge. Database Triggers also support custom error\nhandling, to reduce Trigger suspensions due to non-critical errors.",
